Package org.team21.game.models.order

Class BlockadeOrderTest

java.lang.Object
org.team21.game.models.order.BlockadeOrderTest
public class BlockadeOrderTest extends Object
This class tests the Blockade Order. It includes tests for executing the order and validating the command for different scenarios. The scenarios include cases where the target country belongs to the same player and where it does not belong to the player.
Author:
Tejasvi
